Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         dbus,
         alsa-utils
Recommends: pulseaudio | pipewire-pulse, ydotool
Description: Voice assistant that listens on Linux
 voxtty is a voice-controlled assistant for Linux with wake-word mode switching.
 Say "code mode" to switch, "hey assistant" for AI help, or "dictation mode"
 for typing. Choose your backend: local Whisper for privacy or cloud AI for
 advanced features. System tray control, realtime streaming, and system-wide
 typing via ydotool.
